This is the bestest thing i have ever made in my life , because this is not just a contest , This is my real life story which is actual happened with me.  @forever52india @forever52bharat @forever52makeupofficial 

INSHORT : “Apne liye puri duniya se ladna asaan h lekin apne hi parivaar se apne liye ladna bhot muskil” .

RELATIBILITY : A big shoutout to all the people who grew up with emotionally unsupportive parents. I know it’s hard to hear other people talk about how supportive their families are, all while you are basically guiding yourself through life. BUT YOU’VE managed to overcome everything life has thrown at you all on your own. so if that doesn’t make you realise that you have the power to literally accomplish anything. i don’t know what will. you are stronger and braver than you realise!! 

I would like to thank you @forever52india for giving this golden opportunity to all the creators to the extent. i can’t thankyou enough that i have made this kind of short real story based AD FILM for the contest. 

I have given my best for this! And i hope you guys like my ENTRY.
